"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Note:</emph> Other <literal>ScriptForge</literal> undescribed modules are reserved for internal use. Their content is subject to change without notice."
msgstr "<emph>ໝາຍເຫດ:</emph> ໂມດູນ <literal>ScriptForge</literal> ອື່ນໆທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ອະທິບາຍໄວ້ແມ່ນສະຫງວນໄວ້ສຳລັບໃຊ້ພາຍໃນເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ເນື້ອໃນອາດຈະມີການປ່ຽນແປງໂດຍບໍ່ໄດ້ແຈ້ງໃຫ້ຊາບລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. uzETY
#: lib_ScriptForge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"lib_ScriptForge.xhp\n"
"par_id851506659675843\n"
"help.text"
msgid "All <literal>ScriptForge</literal> Basic routines or identifiers that are prefixed with an underscore character \"_\" are reserved for internal use. They are not meant be used in Basic macros or Python scripts."
msgstr "ຣູທີນ ຫຼື ຕົວລະບຸ Basic ຂອງ <literal>ScriptForge</literal> ທັງໝົດທີ່ຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍຂີດກ້ອງ \"_\" ແມ່ນສະຫງວນໄວ້ສຳລັບໃຊ້ພາຍໃນ. ພວກມັນບໍ່ໄດ້ມີໄວ້ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນມາໂຄຣ Basic ຫຼື ສະຄຣິບ Python."

