msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id241619032289964\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Get access to the database contained in a Base document."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າເຖິງຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານ Base."

