"help.text"
msgid "To learn more about form documents, refer to <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_formdocument.xhp\"><literal>ScriptForge.FormDocument</literal> service</link> help page."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຮຽນຮູ້ເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບເອກະສານຟອມ, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງທີ່ໜ້າຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_formdocument.xhp\">ການບໍລິການ <literal>ScriptForge.FormDocument</literal></link>."

#. gCGqW
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id191619037523467\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Depending on the parameters provided this method will return:"
msgstr "ຂຶ້ນຢູ່ກັບພາຣາມິເຕີທີ່ລະບຸ, ວິທີການນີ້ຈະສົ່ງຄືນ:"

#. HqFmT
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id781619037575043\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A zero-based Array with the names of all the forms contained in a form document (if the <literal>Form</literal> argument is absent)"
msgstr "ອາເຣທີ່ເລີ່ມຈາກສູນທີ່ມີຊື່ຂອງທຸກຟອມທີ່ຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານຟອມ (ຖ້າບໍ່ມີອາຄິວເມັ້ນ <literal>Form</literal>)"

#. Q4Had
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id111619037577804\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A <literal>SFDocuments.Form</literal> object representing the form specified in the <literal>Form</literal> argument."
msgstr "ວັດຖຸ <literal>SFDocuments.Form</literal> ທີ່ເປັນຕົວແທນຂອງຟອມທີ່ລະບຸໃນອາຄິວເມັ້ນ <literal>Form</literal>."

#. cifGC
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id81692554166191\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The method <literal>Forms</literal> is deprecated since %PRODUCTNAME 7.6. Although it is still available, it may be removed from the <literal>Base</literal> service in a future release. Use the <literal>Forms</literal> method from the <literal>FormDocument</literal> service instead."
msgstr "ວິທີການ <literal>Forms</literal> ຖືກຍົກເລີກການໃຊ້ແລ້ວຕັ້ງແຕ່ %PRODUCTNAME 7.6. ເຖິງວ່າມັນຍັງມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຢູ່, ແຕ່ມັນອາດຈະຖືກເອົາອອກຈາກການບໍລິການ <literal>Base</literal> ໃນລຸ້ນຕໍ່ໄປ. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ວິທີການ <literal>Forms</literal> ຈາກການບໍລິການ <literal>FormDocument</literal> ແທນ."

#. pEtwt
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id861619037838260\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>formdocument:</emph> The name of a valid form document as a case-sensitive string."
msgstr "<emph>formdocument:</emph> ຊື່ຂອງເອກະສານຟອມທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ ເຊິ່ງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງລະບຸຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. L3csm
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id281619037857187\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>form:</emph> The name or index number of the form stored in the form document. If this argument is absent, the method will return a list with the names of all forms available in the form document."
msgstr "<emph>form:</emph> ຊື່ ຫຼື ເລກດັດຊະນີຂອງຟອມທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໃນເອກະສານຟອມ. ຖ້າບໍ່ມີອາຄິວເມັ້ນນີ້, ວິທີການຈະສົ່ງຄືນລາຍຊື່ຂອງທຸກຟອມທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານຟອມ."

#. K4nQh
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id921619437863617\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Although it is possible to use index numbers to refer to forms, this is only recommended when there is just one form in the form document. If there are two or more forms, it is preferable to use the form name instead."
msgstr "ເຖິງວ່າຈະສາມາດໃຊ້ເລກດັດຊະນີເພື່ອອ້າງອີງເຖິງຟອມໄດ້, ແຕ່ຂໍແນະນຳໃຫ້ໃຊ້ວິທີນີ້ສະເພາະເມື່ອມີພຽງຟອມດຽວໃນເອກະສານຟອມ. ຖ້າມີສອງຟອມຂຶ້ນໄປ, ຄວນໃຊ້ຊື່ຂອງຟອມແທນ."

#. DoxrV
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id21623104676805\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The first line of the example below returns a list of all forms in the form document \"myFormDocument\". The second line returns an instance of the Form service representing the form \"myForm\"."
msgstr "ແຖວທຳອິດຂອງຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ຈະສົ່ງຄືນລາຍຊື່ຂອງທຸກຟອມໃນເອກະສານຟອມ \"myFormDocument\". ແຖວທີສອງຈະສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງການບໍລິການ Form ທີ່ເປັນຕົວແທນຂອງຟອມ \"myForm\"."

#. MGjWj
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id371619098340303\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns an instance of the <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_database.xhp\"><literal>Database</literal> service</link> that allows the execution of SQL commands on the database defined and/or stored in the current Base document"
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_database.xhp\">ການບໍລິການ <literal>Database</literal></link> ທີ່ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສາມາດປະຕິບັດຄຳສັ່ງ SQL ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກຳນົດ ແລະ/ຫຼື ເກັບໄວ້ໃນເອກະສານ Base ປະຈຸບັນ."

#. 9Bncy
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id731619098073221\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>user, password:</emph> Optional login parameters as strings. The default value for both parameters is an empty string \"\"."
msgstr "<emph>user, password:</emph> ພາຣາມິເຕີການເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ (ສາມາດເລືອກລະບຸໄດ້) ເຊິ່ງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງທັງສອງພາຣາມິເຕີແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມວ່າງ \"\"."

#. UbzRD
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"bas_id631615147843278\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' User and password are supplied below, if needed"
msgstr "' ລະບຸຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ ແລະ ລະຫັດຜ່ານລຸ່ມນີ້ ຖ້າຈຳເປັນ"

#. XBJVn
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"bas_id921599408791887\n"
"help.text"
msgid "'   ... Run queries, SQL statements, ..."
msgstr "'   ... ເປີດການສອບຖາມ, ຄຳສັ່ງ SQL, ..."

#. eRmFK
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"pyc_id351623104861223\n"
"help.text"
msgid "#   ... Run queries, SQL statements, ..."
msgstr "#   ... ເປີດການສອບຖາມ, ຄຳສັ່ງ SQL, ..."

#. mBphD
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id871619098478513\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns <literal>True</literal> if the specified <literal>FormDocument</literal> is  currently open."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າ <literal>FormDocument</literal> ທີ່ລະບຸຖືກເປີດຢູ່ໃນຂະນະນີ້."

#. njjFg
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id981619098545701\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>formdocument:</emph> The name of a <literal>FormDocument</literal> to be checked, as a case-sensitive string."
msgstr "<emph>formdocument:</emph> ຊື່ຂອງ <literal>FormDocument</literal> ທີ່ຈະກວດສອບ, ເຊິ່ງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງລະບຸຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. vzCvY
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id801619099743199\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens the specified <literal>FormDocument</literal> either in normal or in design mode. This method returns a <literal>FormDocument</literal> service instance corresponding to the specified form document."
msgstr "ເປີດ <literal>FormDocument</literal> ທີ່ລະບຸບໍ່ວ່າຈະຢູ່ໃນໂໝດປົກກະຕິ ຫຼື ໂໝດອອກແບບ. ວິທີການນີ້ຈະສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງການບໍລິການ <literal>FormDocument</literal> ທີ່ກົງກັບເອກະສານຟອມທີ່ລະບຸ."

#. UEGjL
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id451619100075330\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the form document is already open, it is activated without changing its mode."
msgstr "ຖ້າເອກະສານຟອມຖືກເປີດຢູ່ແລ້ວ, ມັນຈະຖືກເປີດຂຶ້ນມາໂດຍບໍ່ມີການປ່ຽນໂໝດ."

#. ZGYRs
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id651692554712005\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the specified form document does not exist, then <literal>Nothing</literal> is returned."
msgstr "ຖ້າບໍ່ມີເອກະສານຟອມທີ່ລະບຸ, ມັນຈະສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>Nothing</literal>."

#. dUE6w
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id941619099797810\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>formDocument:</emph> The name of the <literal>FormDocument</literal> to be opened, as a case-sensitive string."
msgstr "<emph>formDocument:</emph> ຊື່ຂອງ <literal>FormDocument</literal> ທີ່ຈະເປີດ, ເຊິ່ງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງລະບຸຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. Coxpu
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id981619099816849\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>designmode:</emph> If this argument is <literal>True</literal> the <literal>FormDocument</literal> will be opened in design mode."
msgstr "<emph>designmode:</emph> ຖ້າອາຄິວເມັ້ນນີ້ເປັນ <literal>True</literal>, <literal>FormDocument</literal> ຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດອອກແບບ."

#. B29ng
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id251619100191992\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Most form documents are stored in the root of the Base document and they can be opened simply using their names, as in the example below:"
msgstr "ເອກະສານຟອມສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນສ່ວນຫຼັກຂອງເອກະສານ Base ແລະ ສາມາດເປີດໄດ້ງ່າຍໆໂດຍໃຊ້ຊື່ຂອງພວກມັນ, ດັ່ງໃນຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້:"

#. ACLqQ
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id351619100327505\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If form documents are organized in folders, it becomes necessary to include the folder name to specify the form document to be opened, as illustrated in the following example:"
msgstr "ຖ້າເອກະສານຟອມຖືກຈັດລະບຽບໄວ້ໃນໂຟນເດີ, ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງລວມເອົາຊື່ໂຟນເດີເພື່ອລະບຸເອກະສານຟອມທີ່ຈະເປີດ, ດັ່ງທີ່ສະແດງໃນຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#. FfnCL
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id31599490604484\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens the Data View window of the specified query and returns an instance of the <literal>Datasheet</literal> service."
msgstr "ເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງການສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນ (Data View) ຂອງການສອບຖາມທີ່ລະບຸ ແລະ ສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງການບໍລິການ <literal>Datasheet</literal>."

#. y7bbd
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id281671113374329\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The query can be opened either in normal or design mode."
msgstr "ການສອບຖາມສາມາດເປີດໄດ້ບໍ່ວ່າຈະຢູ່ໃນໂໝດປົກກະຕິ ຫຼື ໂໝດອອກແບບ."

#. PteVF
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id801671111609985\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the query is already open, its Data View window will be made active."
msgstr "ຖ້າການສອບຖາມຖືກເປີດຢູ່ແລ້ວ, ໜ້າຕ່າງການສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງມັນຈະຖືກເປີດຂຶ້ນມາ."

#. PD6CC
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id521671113436716\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Closing the Base document will cause the Data View window to be closed as well."
msgstr "ການປິດເອກະສານ Base ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ໜ້າຕ່າງການສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນຖືກປິດລົງນຳ."

#. h53Y2
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id701599490609511\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>queryname</emph>: The name of an existing query as a case-sensitive String."
msgstr "<emph>queryname</emph>: ຊື່ຂອງການສອບຖາມທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ ເຊິ່ງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງລະບຸຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. tfZPA
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id461671113939669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>designmode</emph>: If this argument is set to <literal>True</literal> the query is opened in design mode. Otherwise it is opened in normal mode (Default = <literal>False</literal>)."
msgstr "<emph>designmode</emph>: ຖ້າອາຄິວເມັ້ນນີ້ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ <literal>True</literal>, ການສອບຖາມຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດອອກແບບ. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ມັນຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດປົກກະຕິ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = <literal>False</literal>)."

#. f8xGi
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id31599490604787\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens the Data View window of the specified table and returns an instance of the <literal>Datasheet</literal> service."
msgstr "ເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງການສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງຕາຕະລາງທີ່ລະບຸ ແລະ ສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງການບໍລິການ <literal>Datasheet</literal>."

#. kJ7je
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id281671113374441\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The table can be opened either in normal or design mode."
msgstr "ຕາຕະລາງສາມາດເປີດໄດ້ບໍ່ວ່າຈະຢູ່ໃນໂໝດປົກກະຕິ ຫຼື ໂໝດອອກແບບ."

#. mLCsE
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id801671111609395\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the table is already open, its Data View window will be made active."
msgstr "ຖ້າຕາຕະລາງຖືກເປີດຢູ່ແລ້ວ, ໜ້າຕ່າງການສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງມັນຈະຖືກເປີດຂຶ້ນມາ."

#. CewtN
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id521671113436658\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Closing the Base document will cause the Data View window to be closed as well."
msgstr "ການປິດເອກະສານ Base ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ໜ້າຕ່າງການສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນຖືກປິດລົງນຳ."

#. 7Ub95
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id701599490609099\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>tablename</emph>: The name of an existing table as a case-sensitive String."
msgstr "<emph>tablename</emph>: ຊື່ຂອງຕາຕະລາງທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ ເຊິ່ງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງລະບຸຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. E2TZg
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id461671113939471\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>designmode</emph>: If this argument is set to <literal>True</literal> the table is opened in design mode. Otherwise it is opened in normal mode (Default = <literal>False</literal>)."
msgstr "<emph>designmode</emph>: ຖ້າອາຄິວເມັ້ນນີ້ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ <literal>True</literal>, ຕາຕະລາງຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດອອກແບບ. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ມັນຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດປົກກະຕິ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = <literal>False</literal>)."

#. zzgBi
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id156589200121138\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This method sends the content of the given form document to a default printer or a printer defined by the <literal>SetPrinter()</literal> method."
msgstr "ວິທີການນີ້ຈະສົ່ງເນື້ອໃນຂອງເອກະສານຟອມທີ່ກຳນົດໄປຍັງເຄື່ອງພິມເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ຫຼື ເຄື່ອງພິມທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍວິທີການ <literal>SetPrinter()</literal>."

#. oeDSX
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id981611169416934\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns <literal>True</literal> if the document was successfully printed."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າພິມເອກະສານສຳເລັດ."

#. yqC7c
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id81692554166367\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The method <literal>PrintOut</literal> is deprecated since %PRODUCTNAME 7.6. Although it is still available, it may be removed from the <literal>Base</literal> service in a future release. Use the <literal>PrintOut</literal> method from the <literal>FormDocument</literal> service instead."
msgstr "ວິທີການ <literal>PrintOut</literal> ຖືກຍົກເລີກການໃຊ້ແລ້ວຕັ້ງແຕ່ %PRODUCTNAME 7.6. ເຖິງວ່າມັນຍັງມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຢູ່, ແຕ່ມັນອາດຈະຖືກເອົາອອກຈາກການບໍລິການ <literal>Base</literal> ໃນລຸ້ນຕໍ່ໄປ. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ວິທີການ <literal>PrintOut</literal> ຈາກການບໍລິການ <literal>FormDocument</literal> ແທນ."

#. pwm7n
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id368519200121646\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>formdocument</emph>: A valid document form name as a case-sensitive string. The form document must be open. It is activated by the method."
msgstr "<emph>formdocument</emph>: ຊື່ເອກະສານຟອມທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ ເຊິ່ງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງລະບຸຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ເອກະສານຟອມຕ້ອງຖືກເປີດຢູ່ ແລະ ຈະຖືກເປີດຂຶ້ນມາໂດຍວິທີການນີ້."

#. nRU4K
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id211635436910093\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>pages</emph>: The pages to print as a string, like in the user interface. Example: \"1-4;10;15-18\". Default is all pages."
msgstr "<emph>pages</emph>: ໜ້າທີ່ຈະພິມໃນຮູບແບບຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ເຊັ່ນດຽວກັບໃນສ່ວນຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້. ຕົວຢ່າງ: \"1-4;10;15-18\". ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນທຸກໜ້າ."

#. UxDTL
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id141635436912146\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>copies</emph>: The number of copies. Default is 1."
msgstr "<emph>copies</emph>: ຈຳນວນສຳເນົາ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 1."

#. gDM4C
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id911298505147502\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Define the printer options for a form document. The form document must be open."
msgstr "ກຳນົດຕົວເລືອກເຄື່ອງພິມສຳລັບເອກະສານຟອມ. ເອກະສານຟອມຕ້ອງຖືກເປີດຢູ່."

#. owLwe
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id381651114800685\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns <literal>True</literal> when successful."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>True</literal> ເມື່ອສຳເລັດ."

#. s5k6j
#: sf_base.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_base.xhp\n"
"par_id81692554166449\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The method <literal>SetPrinter</literal> is deprecated since %PRODUCTNAME 7.6. Although it is still available, it may be removed from the <literal>Base</literal> service in a future release. Use the <literal>SetPrinter</literal> method from the <literal>Document</literal> service instead."
msgstr "ວິທີການ <literal>SetPrinter</literal> ຖືກຍົກເລີກການໃຊ້ແລ້ວຕັ້ງແຕ່ %PRODUCTNAME 7.6. ເຖິງວ່າມັນຍັງມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຢູ່, ແຕ່ມັນອາດຈະຖືກເອົາອອກຈາກການບໍລິການ <literal>Base</literal> ໃນລຸ້ນຕໍ່ໄປ. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ວິທີການ <literal>SetPrinter</literal> ຈາກການບໍລິການ <literal>Document</literal> ແທນ."

