#. P4TEF
#: sf_database.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_database.xhp\n"
"par_id391701355293522\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This method is ignored if commits are done automatically after each SQL statement, i.e. the database is set to the default auto-commit mode."
msgstr "ວິທີການນີ້ຈະຖືກລະເລີຍຖ້າມີການ commit ອັດຕະໂນມັດຫຼັງຈາກທຸກຄຳສັ່ງ SQL, ນັ້ນຄືຖານຂໍ້ມູນຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນໂໝດ auto-commit ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

