"help.text"
msgid "The examples below in Basic and Python display the <literal>dlgConsole</literal> dialog that belongs to the <literal>ScriptForge</literal> shared library:"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ໃນ Basic ແລະ Python ສະແດງໄດອາລັອກ <literal>dlgConsole</literal> ເຊິ່ງເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຫ້ອງສະໝຸດສ່ວນກາງ <literal>ScriptForge</literal>:"

#. mqjFF
