#. Qsut4
#: sf_dictionary.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_dictionary.xhp\n"
"bas_id251765034282638\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' The keys are case-sensitive, hence the second argument is <literal>True</literal>"
msgstr "' ຄີຈະແຍກຕົວອັກສອນນ້ອຍ-ໃຫຍ່, ດັ່ງນັ້ນອາຄິວເມັນທີສອງຈຶ່ງເປັນ <literal>True</literal>"

#. BghTS
#: sf_dictionary.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_dictionary.xhp\n"
"par_id71158288562139\n"
"help.text"
msgid "It is recommended to free resources after use:"
msgstr "ແນະນຳໃຫ້ຄືນຊັບພະຍາກອນ (free resources) ຫຼັງຈາກໃຊ້ງານແລ້ວ:"

#. gpGvc
#: sf_dictionary.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_dictionary.xhp\n"
"par_id551626869252987\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The example below creates an empty instance of the <literal>Dictionary</literal> service and uses the Python native <literal>update</literal> method to populate it with the contents of a Python <literal>dict</literal> object."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ຈະສ້າງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຫວ່າງເປົ່າຂອງບໍລິການ <literal>Dictionary</literal> ແລະ ໃຊ້ວິທີການ <literal>update</literal> ຂອງ Python ເອງເພື່ອຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນໃສ່ດ້ວຍເນື້ອໃນຈາກວັດຖຸ <literal>dict</literal> ຂອງ Python."

#. AGLAS
#: sf_dictionary.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_dictionary.xhp\n"
"pyc_id61626869417128\n"
