#. G4WCE
#: sf_dictionary.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_dictionary.xhp\n"
"par_id981626869718081\n"
"help.text"
msgid "It is possible to create an instance of the <literal>Dictionary</literal> service using a Python <literal>dict</literal> object as argument as shown in the following example."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງບໍລິການ <literal>Dictionary</literal> ໂດຍໃຊ້ວັດຖຸ <literal>dict</literal> ຂອງ Python ເປັນອາຄິວເມັນ ດັ່ງທີ່ສະແດງໃນຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້."

#. ymvAC
#: sf_dictionary.xhp
msgctxt ""
