msgstr "ບໍ່"

#. RyJkE
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id581584978715701\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The error message text."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#. Wcy7s
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id241610652688334\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Default value is \"\" or a string containing the Basic run-time error message."
msgstr "ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ \"\" ຫຼື ສາຍອັກຂະລະທີ່ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມຜິດພາດໃນເວລາເຮັດວຽກຂອງ Basic."

#. BT7GF
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id211584978211383\n"
"help.text"
msgid "No"
msgstr "ບໍ່"

#. AnFVG
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id691584978211774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The code of the error. It can be a numeric value or text."
msgstr "ລະຫັດຂອງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ. ມັນສາມາດເປັນຄ່າຕົວເລກ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. dCADC
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id151610652632828\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Default value is 0 or the numeric value corresponding to the Basic run-time error code."
msgstr "ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 0 ຫຼື ຄ່າຕົວເລກທີ່ກົງກັບລະຫັດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນເວລາເຮັດວຽກຂອງ Basic."

#. uLE2Q
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id671584978666689\n"
"help.text"
msgid "No"
msgstr "ບໍ່"

#. G3q2n
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id951584978666296\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The location in the code where the error occurred. It can be a numeric value or text."
msgstr "ຕຳແໜ່ງໃນລະຫັດທີ່ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ. ມັນສາມາດເປັນຄ່າຕົວເລກ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. kBXGC
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id681610652723345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Default value is 0 or the code line number for a standard Basic run-time error."
msgstr "ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 0 ຫຼື ໝາຍເລກແຖວລະຫັດສຳລັບຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນເວລາເຮັດວຽກມາດຕະຖານຂອງ Basic."

#. mnFGS
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id461584978880380\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Raising or clearing an <literal>Exception</literal> resets its properties."
msgstr "ການສ້າງ (Raising) ຫຼື ການລຶບລ້າງ (clearing) <literal>Exception</literal> ຈະຕັ້ງຄ່າຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງມັນໃໝ່."

#. ssXEB
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id881608131596153\n"
"help.text"
msgid "List of Methods in the Exception Service"
msgstr "ລາຍຊື່ວິທີການໃນບໍລິການ Exception"

#. CDgEM
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id271579683706571\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Resets the current error status and clears the <literal>SF_Exception</literal> properties."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າສະຖານະຂໍ້ຜິດພາດປັດຈຸບັນໃໝ່ ແລະ ລຶບລ້າງຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງ <literal>SF_Exception</literal>."

#. 7jFLi
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id701610654263121\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following example shows how to catch a division-by-zero exception, whose error code is 11."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນວິທີການດັກຈັບຂໍ້ຍົກເວັ້ນການຫານດ້ວຍສູນ, ເຊິ່ງມີລະຫັດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດແມ່ນ 11."

#. JhADn
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"bas_id51587215508130\n"
"help.text"
msgid "'If division by zero, ignore the error"
msgstr "'ຖ້າມີການຫານດ້ວຍສູນ, ໃຫ້ລະເລີຍຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ"

#. DHZ5A
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id201610654368082\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For a complete list of Basic run-time error codes, refer to <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/01030300.xhp\">Debugging a Basic Program</link>."
msgstr "ສຳລັບລາຍຊື່ຄົບຖ້ວນຂອງລະຫັດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນເວລາເຮັດວຽກຂອງ Basic, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງທີ່ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/01030300.xhp\">ການດີບັກໂປຣແກຣມ Basic</link>."

#. efEEX
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id651598718179382\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Displays the console messages in a modal or non-modal dialog. In both modes, all the past messages issued by a <literal>DebugPrint()</literal> method or resulting from an exception are displayed. In non-modal mode, subsequent entries are added automatically."
msgstr "ສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມຄອນໂຊລໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມໂຕ້ຕອບແບບໂມດອລ (modal) ຫຼື ບໍ່ແມ່ນໂມດອລ (non-modal). ໃນທັງສອງໂໝດ, ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຜ່ານມາທັງໝົດທີ່ອອກໂດຍວິທີການ <literal>DebugPrint()</literal> ຫຼື ທີ່ເປັນຜົນມາຈາກຂໍ້ຍົກເວັ້ນຈະຖືກສະແດງ. ໃນໂໝດທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນໂມດອລ, ລາຍການຕໍ່ໆໄປຈະຖືກເພີ່ມໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. KKgdp
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id161598718286205\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the console is already open, when non-modal, it is brought to the front."
msgstr "ຖ້າຄອນໂຊລຖືກເປີດຢູ່ແລ້ວ, ເມື່ອຢູ່ໃນໂໝດທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນໂມດອລ, ມັນຈະຖືກນຳມາໄວ້ທາງໜ້າ."

#. ypzYc
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id801598718629151\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A modal console can only be closed by the user. A non-modal console can either be closed by the user or upon macro termination."
msgstr "ຄອນໂຊລແບບໂມດອລສາມາດປິດໄດ້ໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ຄອນໂຊລແບບທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນໂມດອລສາມາດປິດໄດ້ໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ ຫຼື ເມື່ອແມັກໂຄຣສິ້ນສຸດການເຮັດວຽກ."

#. HUgnb
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id511598718179819\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>modal</emph>: Determine if the console window is modal (<literal>True</literal>) or non-modal (<literal>False</literal>). Default value is <literal>True</literal>."
msgstr "<emph>modal</emph>: ກຳນົດວ່າປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຄອນໂຊລເປັນແບບໂມດອລ (<literal>True</literal>) ຫຼື ບໍ່ແມ່ນໂມດອລ (<literal>False</literal>). ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ <literal>True</literal>."

#. xu6FA
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id641587215098903\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Clears the console keeping an optional number of recent messages. If the console is activated in non-modal mode, it is refreshed."
msgstr "ລຶບລ້າງຄອນໂຊລໂດຍເກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມຫຼ້າສຸດໄວ້ຕາມຈຳນວນທີ່ກຳນົດ (ທາງເລືອກ). ຖ້າຄອນໂຊລຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ໃນໂໝດທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນໂມດອລ, ມັນຈະຖືກຣີເຟຣຊ (refresh)."

#. SE7ei
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id351587215098527\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>keep</emph>: The number of recent messages to be kept. Default value is 0."
msgstr "<emph>keep</emph>: ຈຳນວນຂໍ້ຄວາມຫຼ້າສຸດທີ່ຈະເກັບໄວ້. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 0."

#. GLEVv
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id521610655023824\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following example clears the console keeping the 10 most recent messages."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ລຶບລ້າງຄອນໂຊລໂດຍເກັບ 10 ຂໍ້ຄວາມຫຼ້າສຸດໄວ້."

#. 4LD2d
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id281587218077400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Exports the contents of the console to a text file. If the file already exists and the console is not empty, it will be overwritten without warning. Returns <literal>True</literal> if successful."
msgstr "ສົ່ງອອກເນື້ອຫາຂອງຄອນໂຊລໄປເປັນໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ ແລະ ຄອນໂຊລບໍ່ຫວ່າງເປົ່າ, ມັນຈະຖືກຂຽນທັບໂດຍບໍ່ມີການແຈ້ງເຕືອນ. ສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສຳເລັດ."

#. cAusu
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id851587218077862\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>filename</emph>: The name of the text file the console should be dumped into. The name is expressed according to the current <literal>FileNaming</literal> property of the <literal>SF_FileSystem</literal> service. By default, <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/00000002.xhp\">URL notation</link> and the native operating system's format are both admitted."
msgstr "<emph>filename</emph>: ຊື່ຂອງໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຈະສົ່ງເນື້ອຫາໃນຄອນໂຊລລົງໄປ. ຊື່ຈະຖືກສະແດງຕາມຄຸນສົມບັດ <literal>FileNaming</literal> ປັດຈຸບັນຂອງບໍລິການ <literal>SF_FileSystem</literal>. ໂດຍຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ທັງ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/00000002.xhp\">ຮູບແບບ URL</link> ແລະ ຮູບແບບຂອງລະບົບປະຕິບັດການຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

#. F3tVM
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id701621043185177\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Concatenates all the arguments into a single human-readable string and displays it in a <literal>MsgBox</literal> with an Information icon and an OK button."
msgstr "ລວມຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງທັງໝົດເຂົ້າເປັນສາຍອັກຂະລະດຽວທີ່ມະນຸດສາມາດອ່ານໄດ້ ແລະ ສະແດງມັນໃນ <literal>MsgBox</literal> ພ້ອມກັບໄອຄອນຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ປຸ່ມ OK."

#. KaGM6
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id791621097689492\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The final string is also added to the Console."
msgstr "ສາຍອັກຂະລະສຸດທ້າຍກໍຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນ Console ຄືກັນ."

#. QhRgF
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id481587218636884\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>arg0[, arg1, ...]</emph>: Any number of arguments of any type."
msgstr "<emph>arg0[, arg1, ...]</emph>: ຈຳນວນຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງໃດໆກໍໄດ້ຂອງປະເພດໃດກໍໄດ້."

#. 2qser
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id281587218637490\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Assembles all the given arguments into a single human-readable string and adds it as a new entry in the console."
msgstr "ຮວບຮວມຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງທັງໝົດທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້ເຂົ້າເປັນສາຍອັກຂະລະດຽວທີ່ມະນຸດສາມາດອ່ານໄດ້ ແລະ ເພີ່ມມັນເປັນລາຍການໃໝ່ໃນຄອນໂຊລ."

#. mUSEP
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id481587218637988\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>arg0[, arg1, ...]</emph>: Any number of arguments of any type."
msgstr "<emph>arg0[, arg1, ...]</emph>: ຈຳນວນຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງໃດໆກໍໄດ້ຂອງປະເພດໃດກໍໄດ້."

#. sCSES
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id111621624672183\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Displays the list of arguments in a readable form in the platform console. Arguments are separated by a TAB character (simulated by spaces)."
msgstr "ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ຂອງຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງໃນຮູບແບບທີ່ອ່ານໄດ້ໃນຄອນໂຊລຂອງແພລັດຟອມ. ຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງຈະຖືກແຍກດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນ TAB (ຈຳລອງໂດຍການໃຊ້ຍະຫວ່າງ)."

#. ujSFu
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id841621426229467\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The same string is added to the ScriptForge debug console."
msgstr "ສາຍອັກຂະລະດຽວກັນນັ້ນກໍຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນຄອນໂຊລດີບັກຂອງ ScriptForge ຄືກັນ."

#. kzBDb
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id551655563148866\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If <link href=\"https://extensions.libreoffice.org/en/extensions/show/apso-alternative-script-organizer-for-python\">Python shell (APSO)</link> is active, <literal>PythonPrint</literal> content is written to APSO console in place of the platform console."
msgstr "ຖ້າ <link href=\"https://extensions.libreoffice.org/en/extensions/show/apso-alternative-script-organizer-for-python\">Python shell (APSO)</link> ມີການເຄື່ອນໄຫວ, ເນື້ອຫາ <literal>PythonPrint</literal> ຈະຖືກຂຽນລົງໃນຄອນໂຊລ APSO ແທນທີ່ຄອນໂຊລຂອງແພລັດຟອມ."

#. ixNfF
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id391126449167833\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>arg0[, arg1, ...]</emph>: Any number of arguments of any type. The maximum length of each individual argument is 1024 characters."
msgstr "<emph>arg0[, arg1, ...]</emph>: ຈຳນວນຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງໃດໆກໍໄດ້ຂອງປະເພດໃດກໍໄດ້. ຄວາມຍາວສູງສຸດຂອງແຕ່ລະຂໍ້ໂຕ້ແຍ້ງແມ່ນ 1024 ຕົວອັກສອນ."

#. U88JC
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id261123015276160\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Python use a <literal>print</literal> statement to print to the APSO console or use the <literal>DebugPrint</literal> method to print to ScriptForge's console."
msgstr "ໃນ Python ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ <literal>print</literal> ເພື່ອພິມລົງໃນຄອນໂຊລ APSO ຫຼື ໃຊ້ວິທີການ <literal>DebugPrint</literal> ເພື່ອພິມລົງໃນຄອນໂຊລຂອງ ScriptForge."

#. CUoch
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id111621426672183\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens an APSO Python shell as a non-modal window. The Python script keeps running after the shell is opened. The output from <literal>print</literal> statements inside the script are shown in the shell."
msgstr "ເປີດ APSO Python shell ເປັນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມແບບບໍ່ແມ່ນໂມດອລ. ສະຄຣິບ Python ຍັງຄົງເຮັດວຽກຕໍ່ໄປຫຼັງຈາກເປີດ shell ແລ້ວ. ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຈາກຄຳສັ່ງ <literal>print</literal> ພາຍໃນສະຄຣິບຈະຖືກສະແດງຢູ່ໃນ shell."

#. f9ZzM
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id841621426922467\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Only a single instance of the APSO Python shell can be opened at any time. Hence, if a Python shell is already open, then calling this method will have no effect."
msgstr "ສາມາດເປີດ APSO Python shell ໄດ້ພຽງແຕ່ອັນດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນໃນແຕ່ລະຄັ້ງ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ຖ້າ Python shell ຖືກເປີດຢູ່ແລ້ວ, ການເອີ້ນໃຊ້ວິທີການນີ້ຈະບໍ່ມີຜົນຫຍັງ."

#. KGi8B
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id391621449167833\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>variables</emph>: a Python dictionary with variable names and values that will be passed on to the APSO Python shell. By default all local variables are passed using Python's builtin <literal>locals()</literal> function."
msgstr "<emph>variables</emph>: ດິກຊັນນາຣີ Python ທີ່ມີຊື່ຕົວປ່ຽນ ແລະ ຄ່າທີ່ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປໃຫ້ APSO Python shell. ໂດຍຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ຕົວປ່ຽນທ້ອງຖິ່ນທັງໝົດຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປໂດຍໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ <literal>locals()</literal> ທີ່ມີມາໃຫ້ໃນ Python."

#. dEdrj
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id402621449167833\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>background</emph>: Background color of the console specified as <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_basic.xhp#RGB\">RGB 24 bits integer value</link>. Default background is that of APSO."
msgstr "<emph>background</emph>: ສີພື້ນຫຼັງຂອງຄອນໂຊລທີ່ລະບຸເປັນ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_basic.xhp#RGB\">ຄ່າເລກຈຳນວນເຕັມ RGB 24 ບິດ</link>. ພື້ນຫຼັງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນຂອງ APSO."

#. GNfJ9
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id513621449167833\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>foreground</emph>: Foreground color of the console specified as <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_basic.xhp#RGB\">RGB 24 bits integer value</link>. Default foreground is that of APSO."
msgstr "<emph>foreground</emph>: ສີຕົວອັກສອນຂອງຄອນໂຊລທີ່ລະບຸເປັນ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_basic.xhp#RGB\">ຄ່າເລກຈຳນວນເຕັມ RGB 24 ບິດ</link>. ສີຕົວອັກສອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນຂອງ APSO."

#. 5HDY8
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id991621449657850\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The example below opens the APSO Python shell passing all global and local variables considering the context where the script is running. Console is displayed with white characters on a black background."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ເປີດ APSO Python shell ໂດຍສົ່ງຕົວປ່ຽນທົ່ວໄປ ແລະ ຕົວປ່ຽນທ້ອງຖິ່ນທັງໝົດໂດຍພິຈາລະນາຈາກສະພາບການທີ່ສະຄຣິບກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກຢູ່. ຄອນໂຊລຈະສະແດງດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນສີຂາວເທິງພື້ນຫຼັງສີດຳ."

#. yUoFK
#: sf_exception.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_exception.xhp\n"
"par_id521621449800348\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When the APSO Python shell is open, any subsequent output printed by the script will be shown in the shell. Hence, the string printed in the example below will be displayed in the Python shell."
msgstr "ເມື່ອ APSO Python shell ຖືກເປີດຢູ່, ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບໃດໆກໍຕາມທີ່ຖືກພິມໂດຍສະຄຣິບຈະຖືກສະແດງຢູ່ໃນ shell. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ສາຍອັກຂະລະທີ່ພິມໃນຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້ຈະຖືກສະແດງຢູ່ໃນ Python shell."

#. 5xNCX
