"par_id421598179770993\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the method is called <emph>without arguments</emph>, then it returns the list of the controls contained in the form. Be aware that the returned list does not contain any subform controls."
msgstr "ຖ້າເມັດທອດຖືກເອີ້ນໃຊ້ <emph>ໂດຍບໍ່ມີອາກິວເມັນ</emph>, ມັນຈະສົ່ງຄືນລາຍການຂອງຕົວຄວບຄຸມ (controls) ທັງໝົດທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຟອມ. ໃຫ້ຮັບຊາບວ່າລາຍການທີ່ສົ່ງຄືນນັ້ນຈະບໍ່ລວມເອົາຕົວຄວບຄຸມຂອງຟອມຍ່ອຍ."

#. SsiUX
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id81598185229301\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the optional <literal>ControlName</literal> argument is provided, the method returns a <literal>FormControl</literal> class instance referring to the specified control."
msgstr "ຖ້າລະບຸອາກິວເມັນທາງເລືອກ <literal>ControlName</literal>, ເມັດທອດຈະສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຄລາດ <literal>FormControl</literal> ທີ່ອ້າງອີງເຖິງຕົວຄວບຄຸມທີ່ລະບຸ."

#. 7CFJU
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id1001584541257789\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>controlname</emph> : A valid control name as a case-sensitive string. If absent, the list of control names is returned as a zero-based array."
msgstr "<emph>controlname</emph> : ຊື່ຕົວຄວບຄຸມທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງໃນຮູບແບບສະຕຣິງທີ່ແຍກຕົວອັກສອນນ້ອຍ-ໃຫຍ່ (case-sensitive). ຖ້າບໍ່ລະບຸ, ລາຍການຊື່ຕົວຄວບຄຸມຈະຖືກສົ່ງຄືນເປັນອາເຣທີ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍສູນ (zero-based array)."

#. PTqJ2
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id291616861407907\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Return a <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_database.xhp\"><literal>SFDatabases</literal>.<literal>Database</literal></link> instance giving access to the execution of SQL commands on the database the current form is connected to and/or that is stored in the current Base document."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄ່າອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_database.xhp\"><literal>SFDatabases</literal>.<literal>Database</literal></link> ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງການປະຕິບັດຄຳສັ່ງ SQL ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຟອມປັດຈຸບັນເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຢູ່ ແລະ/ຫຼື ທີ່ຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນເອກະສານ Base ປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. fZRst
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id991616861417207\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Each form has its own database connection, except in Base documents where they all share the same connection."
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະຟອມມີການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຖານຂໍ້ມູນເປັນຂອງຕົນເອງ, ຍົກເວັ້ນໃນເອກະສານ Base ທີ່ທຸກຟອມຈະໃຊ້ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ດຽວກັນ."

#. wFSWb
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id701616861134906\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>user, password</emph>: The login optional parameters (Default = \"\")."
msgstr "<emph>user, password</emph>: ພາລາມິເຕີທາງເລືອກສຳລັບການເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = \"\")."

#. 83Jju
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id771616861842867\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The form cursor is positioned on the first record. Returns <literal>True</literal> if successful."
msgstr "ຕົວຊີ້ຟອມຖືກກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງໄວ້ທີ່ຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກທຳອິດ. ສົ່ງຄ່າກັບເປັນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສຳເລັດ."

#. rapRE
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id331616863143187\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The form cursor is positioned on the last record. Returns <literal>True</literal> if successful."
msgstr "ຕົວຊີ້ຟອມຖືກກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງໄວ້ທີ່ຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກສຸດທ້າຍ. ສົ່ງຄ່າກັບເປັນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສຳເລັດ."

#. HZELb
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id361616863143954\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The form cursor is positioned on the new record area. Returns <literal>True</literal> if successful."
msgstr "ຕົວຊີ້ຟອມຖືກກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງໄວ້ທີ່ພື້ນທີ່ຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກໃໝ່. ສົ່ງຄ່າກັບເປັນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສຳເລັດ."

#. 2QwcR
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id541616863143461\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The form cursor is positioned on the next record. Returns <literal>True</literal> if successful."
msgstr "ຕົວຊີ້ຟອມຖືກກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງໄວ້ທີ່ຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກຖັດໄປ. ສົ່ງຄ່າກັບເປັນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສຳເລັດ."

#. a2gGn
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id271616863582607\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>offset</emph>: The number of records to go forward (Default = 1)."
msgstr "<emph>offset</emph>: ຈຳນວນຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກທີ່ຈະໄປທາງໜ້າ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = 1)."

#. e6huC
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id616168637945\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The form cursor is positioned on the previous record. Returns <literal>True</literal> if successful."
msgstr "ຕົວຊີ້ຟອມຖືກກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງໄວ້ທີ່ຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກກ່ອນໜ້າ. ສົ່ງຄ່າກັບເປັນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສຳເລັດ."

#. tAnVw
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id751616863794125\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>offset</emph>: The number of records to go backwards (Default = 1)."
msgstr "<emph>offset</emph>: ຈຳນວນຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກທີ່ຈະຖອຍຫຼັງ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = 1)."

#. Kp4Wo
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id811616864216529\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Reloads the current data from the database and refreshes the form. The cursor is positioned on the first record. Returns <literal>True</literal> if successful."
msgstr "ໂຫລດຂໍ້ມູນປັດຈຸບັນຄືນໃໝ່ຈາກຖານຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ຣີເຟຣຊຟອມ. ຕົວຊີ້ຈະຖືກກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງໄວ້ທີ່ຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກທຳອິດ. ສົ່ງຄ່າກັບເປັນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສຳເລັດ."

#. 5gBGr
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id891616864510614\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The value returned by the <literal>Subforms</literal> method depends on the arguments provided:"
msgstr "ຄ່າທີ່ສົ່ງຄືນໂດຍເມັດທອດ <literal>Subforms</literal> ແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບອາກິວເມັນທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້:"

#. 4yG2j
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id951616864510585\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the method is called <emph>without any arguments</emph>, then it returns the list of subforms contained in the current form or subform instance."
msgstr "ຖ້າເມັດທອດຖືກເອີ້ນໃຊ້ <emph>ໂດຍບໍ່ມີອາກິວເມັນໃດໆ</emph>, ມັນຈະສົ່ງຄືນລາຍການຂອງຟອມຍ່ອຍ (subforms) ທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຟອມ ຫຼື ຟອມຍ່ອຍປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. AD3Q6
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id591616864510445\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the optional <literal>subform</literal> argument is provided, the method returns a new <literal>SFDocuments</literal>.<literal>Form</literal> instance based on the specified form/subform name or index."
msgstr "ຖ້າລະບຸອາກິວເມັນທາງເລືອກ <literal>subform</literal>, ເມັດທອດຈະສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ <literal>SFDocuments</literal>.<literal>Form</literal> ໃໝ່ ໂດຍອີງຕາມຊື່ ຫຼື ອິນເດັກຂອງຟອມ/ຟອມຍ່ອຍທີ່ລະບຸ."

#. GCRsS
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id341616864510747\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>subform</emph>: A subform stored in the current <literal>Form</literal> class instance given by its name or index."
msgstr "<emph>subform</emph>: ຟອມຍ່ອຍທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໃນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຄລາດ <literal>Form</literal> ປັດຈຸບັນ ເຊິ່ງລະບຸໂດຍຊື່ ຫຼື ອິນເດັກຂອງມັນ."

#. uKm6R
#: sf_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_form.xhp\n"
"par_id211618230389251\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When this argument is absent, the method returns a list of available subforms as a zero-based array. If the form has a single subform, you can set <literal>subform = 0</literal> to get access to it."
msgstr "ເມື່ອບໍ່ມີອາກິວເມັນນີ້, ເມັດທອດຈະສົ່ງຄືນລາຍການຟອມຍ່ອຍທີ່ມີຢູ່ເປັນອາເຣທີ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍສູນ. ຖ້າຟອມມີຟອມຍ່ອຍພຽງອັນດຽວ, ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດ <literal>subform = 0</literal> ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງມັນໄດ້."

#. CfGgB
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "SFDocuments.FormControl service"
msgstr "ບໍລິການ SFDocuments.FormControl"

#. U4CgG
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"bm_id781582391760253\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"FormControlService\"><link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_formcontrol.xhp\"><literal>SFDocuments</literal>.<literal>FormControl</literal> service</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"FormControlService\"><link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_formcontrol.xhp\">ບໍລິການ <literal>SFDocuments</literal>.<literal>FormControl</literal></link></variable>"

#. XFkrG
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id931583589764919\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <literal>FormControl</literal> service provides access to the controls that belong to a form, a subform or a table control of a <literal>FormDocument</literal>. Each instance of the <literal>FormControl</literal> service refers to a single control in the form. This service allows users to:"
msgstr "ບໍລິການ <literal>FormControl</literal> ໃຫ້ການເຂົ້າເຖິງຕົວຄວບຄຸມ (controls) ທີ່ເປັນຂອງຟອມ, ຟອມຍ່ອຍ ຫຼື ຕົວຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງຂອງ <literal>FormDocument</literal>. ແຕ່ລະອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງບໍລິການ <literal>FormControl</literal> ຈະອ້າງອີງເຖິງຕົວຄວບຄຸມດຽວໃນຟອມ. ບໍລິການນີ້ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດ:"

#. irNFC
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id451618771561326\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Get and set the properties of the control represented by the <literal>FormControl</literal> instance."
msgstr "ເອົາຄ່າ ແລະ ກຳນົດຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງຕົວຄວບຄຸມທີ່ສະແດງໂດຍອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ <literal>FormControl</literal>."

#. S5aH9
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id601618771565183\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Access the current value displayed by the control."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າເຖິງຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນທີ່ສະແດງໂດຍຕົວຄວບຄຸມ."

#. P5xzV
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id981618771567951\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the focus on the desired control."
msgstr "ກຳນົດໂຟກັດໃຫ້ກັບຕົວຄວບຄຸມທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#. LUDRM
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id301616939922857\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To use the <literal>FormControl</literal> service in a particular form, subform or table control, all controls must have unique names."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໃຊ້ບໍລິການ <literal>FormControl</literal> ໃນຟອມ, ຟອມຍ່ອຍ ຫຼື ຕົວຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງໃດໜຶ່ງ, ທຸກໆຕົວຄວບຄຸມຕ້ອງມີຊື່ທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ."

#. JMFEb
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id541618771629112\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Radio buttons that share the same group name must also have unique control names."
msgstr "ປຸ່ມເລືອກ (Radio buttons) ທີ່ໃຊ້ຊື່ກຸ່ມດຽວກັນ ກໍຕ້ອງມີຊື່ຕົວຄວບຄຸມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນນຳອີກ."

#. mAwyv
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id51618771641273\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The main purpose of the <literal>FormControl</literal> service is setting and getting the properties and values displayed by the controls in a form."
msgstr "ຈຸດປະສົງຫຼັກຂອງບໍລິການ <literal>FormControl</literal> ແມ່ນການກຳນົດ ແລະ ການເອົາຄ່າຄຸນສົມບັດ ແລະ ຄ່າຕ່າງໆທີ່ສະແດງໂດຍຕົວຄວບຄຸມໃນຟອມ."

#. egjZu
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id81618774023346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "All controls have a <literal>Value</literal> property. However, its contents will vary according to the control type. For more information, read <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_formcontrol.xhp#hd_id81598540704978\">The <literal>Value</literal> Property</link> below."
msgstr "ທຸກໆຕົວຄວບຄຸມມີຄຸນສົມບັດ <literal>Value</literal>. ເຖິງຢ່າງໃດກໍຕາມ, ເນື້ອໃນຂອງມັນຈະແຕກຕ່າງກັນໄປຕາມປະເພດຂອງຕົວຄວບຄຸມ. ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ, ໃຫ້ອ່ານ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_formcontrol.xhp#hd_id81598540704978\">ຄຸນສົມບັດ <literal>Value</literal></link> ຢູ່ດ້ານລຸ່ມນີ້."

#. kF29h
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id881618771651907\n"
"help.text"
msgid "It is also possible to format the controls via the <literal>XControlModel</literal> and <literal>XControlView</literal> properties."
msgstr "ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ ຍັງສາມາດຈັດຮູບແບບຕົວຄວບຄຸມຜ່ານຄຸນສົມບັດ <literal>XControlModel</literal> ແລະ <literal>XControlView</literal> ໄດ້ນຳອີກ."

#. SGsH8
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id891598188164936\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <literal>SFDocuments.FormControl</literal> service is closely related to the <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_form.xhp\"><literal>SFDocuments.Form</literal></link> service."
msgstr "ບໍລິການ <literal>SFDocuments.FormControl</literal> ແມ່ນມີຄວາມກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຢ່າງໃກ້ຊິດກັບບໍລິການ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_form.xhp\"><literal>SFDocuments.Form</literal></link>."

#. rUEuw
