#. BeDqF
#: sf_formcontrol.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_formcontrol.xhp\n"
"par_id361598174756160\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <literal>FormControl</literal> service is invoked from an existing <literal>Form</literal> service instance through its <literal>Controls</literal> method."
msgstr "ບໍລິການ <literal>FormControl</literal> ຖືກເອີ້ນໃຊ້ຈາກອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ບໍລິການ <literal>Form</literal> ທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວຜ່ານເມັດທອດ <literal>Controls</literal> ຂອງມັນ."

