msgid "Read the section <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_intro.xhp#pythonpath\">Setting PYTHONPATH</link> below in case of errors importing <literal>scriptforge.py</literal> or <literal>uno.py</literal>."
msgstr "ອ່ານພາກ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_intro.xhp#pythonpath\">ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ PYTHONPATH</link> ດ້ານລຸ່ມນີ້ ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນການນຳເຂົ້າ <literal>scriptforge.py</literal> ຫຼື <literal>uno.py</literal>."

#. s54tE
