msgid "' Refers to the DocumentEvent service implemented in the associated SFDocuments library"
msgstr "' ອ້າງອີງເຖິງບໍລິການ DocumentEvent ທີ່ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນໄລບຣາຣີ SFDocuments ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ"

#. DFhat
#: sf_services.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_services.xhp\n"
"bas_id121613492254532\n"
"help.text"
msgid "' Returns the instance of the Document class that fired the event"
msgstr "' ສົ່ງຄືນອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງຄລາສ Document ທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດເຫດການ"

#. zhCyY
#: sf_services.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_services.xhp\n"
"par_id321627570607194\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Python scripts support keyword arguments when calling <literal>CreateScriptService</literal>. The following example illustrates this concept by instantiating the <literal>Timer</literal> and <literal>Document</literal> services using keyword arguments."
msgstr "ສະຄຣິບ Python ຮອງຮັບ keyword arguments ເມື່ອເອີ້ນໃຊ້ <literal>CreateScriptService</literal>. ຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນເຖິງແນວຄິດນີ້ໂດຍການສ້າງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງບໍລິການ <literal>Timer</literal> ແລະ <literal>Document</literal> ໂດຍໃຊ້ keyword arguments."

#. jah7F
#: sf_services.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_services.xhp\n"
"par_id901627576693156\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To make writing Python scripts more fluid, ScriptForge provides the <literal>Basic</literal> service which allows Python scripts to call a collection of methods with the same syntax and meaning as their homonymous native Basic functions."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ການຂຽນສະຄຣິບ Python ມີຄວາມຄ່ອງຕົວຂຶ້ນ, ScriptForge ໄດ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການ <literal>Basic</literal> ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສະຄຣິບ Python ສາມາດເອີ້ນໃຊ້ເມທອດຕ່າງໆທີ່ມີໄວຍາກອນ ແລະ ຄວາມໝາຍຄືກັນກັບຟັງຊັນ Basic ດັ້ງເດີມທີ່ມີຊື່ຄືກັນ."

#. SDQ7m
#: sf_services.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_services.xhp\n"
"par_id41627644806288\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following example instantiates the <literal>Basic</literal> service and calls the <literal>MsgBox</literal> method, which is equivalent to the <literal>MsgBox</literal> function available in Basic:"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ແມ່ນການສ້າງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ຂອງບໍລິການ <literal>Basic</literal> ແລະ ເອີ້ນໃຊ້ເມທອດ <literal>MsgBox</literal>, ເຊິ່ງທຽບເທົ່າກັບຟັງຊັນ <literal>MsgBox</literal> ທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນ Basic:"

#. TFMGE
#: sf_services.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_services.xhp\n"
"par_id581627645023307\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Be aware that the <literal>Basic</literal> service has to be instantiated in Python scripts using the <literal>CreateScriptService</literal> method."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາຮັບຊາບວ່າບໍລິການ <literal>Basic</literal> ຈະຕ້ອງຖືກສ້າງອິນສະແຕນຊ໌ໃນສະຄຣິບ Python ໂດຍໃຊ້ເມທອດ <literal>CreateScriptService</literal>."

#. LCVem
#: sf_session.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_session.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "ScriptForge.Session service"
msgstr "ບໍລິການ ScriptForge.Session"

