#. ygESx
#: sf_session.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_session.xhp\n"
"par_id571582818023245\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Execute the Python script given its location and name, fetch its result if any. Result can be a single value or an array of values."
msgstr "ປະມວນຜົນສະຄຣິບ Python ຕາມຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຊື່ທີ່ລະບຸ, ແລະ ດຶງເອົາຜົນລັບ (ຖ້າມີ). ຜົນລັບອາດເປັນຄ່າດ່ຽວ ຫຼື ອາເຣຂອງຄ່າຕ່າງໆ."

#. SB2gx
#: sf_session.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_session.xhp\n"
"par_id71600856817410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the script is not found, or if it returns nothing, the returned value is <literal>Empty</literal>."
msgstr "ຖ້າບໍ່ພົບສະຄຣິບ ຫຼື ສະຄຣິບບໍ່ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າໃດໆ, ຄ່າທີ່ສົ່ງຄືນມາຈະແມ່ນ <literal>Empty</literal>."

#. 4WTUK
#: sf_session.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_session.xhp\n"
