"help.text"
msgid "<emph>scope</emph>: One of the applicable constants listed <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_session.xhp#properties_toc\">above</link>. The default value is <literal>session.SCRIPTISSHARED</literal>."
msgstr "<emph>scope</emph>: ໜຶ່ງໃນຄ່າຄົງທີ່ທີ່ນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ຕາມທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03/sf_session.xhp#properties_toc\">ຂ້າງເທິງ</link>. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ <literal>session.SCRIPTISSHARED</literal>."

#. ELfda
#: sf_session.xhp
