msgctxt ""
"sf_session.xhp\n"
"par_id961601031043346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>bcc</emph>: A comma-separated list of email addresses (the \"blind carbon copy\" recipients)."
msgstr "<emph>bcc</emph>: ລາຍການທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມລທີ່ຂັ້ນດ້ວຍຈຸດ (ຜູ້ຮັບໃນຊ່ອງ \"blind carbon copy\")."

#. zAkWZ
