#. TFfR3
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id151611951803163\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The first argument of most methods is the string to be considered. It is always passed by reference and left unchanged. Methods such as <literal>Capitalize</literal>, <literal>Escape</literal>, etc return a new string after their execution."
msgstr "ອາຄິວເມນທຳອິດຂອງເມທອດສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ແມ່ນສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະພິຈາລະນາ. ມັນຈະຖືກສົ່ງຜ່ານດ້ວຍການອ້າງອີງ (passed by reference) ແລະ ບໍ່ມີການປ່ຽນແປງຄ່າເດີມ. ເມທອດຕ່າງໆ ເຊັ່ນ <literal>Capitalize</literal>, <literal>Escape</literal>, ແລະ ອື່ນໆ ຈະສົ່ງຄືນສະຕຣິງໃໝ່ຫຼັງຈາກການປະມວນຜົນ."

#. PYcny
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id371627158142730\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Because Python has comprehensive built-in string support, most of the methods in the <literal>String</literal> service are available for Basic scripts only. The methods available for Basic and Python are: <literal>HashStr</literal>, <literal>IsADate</literal>, <literal>IsEmail</literal>, <literal>IsFileName</literal>, <literal>IsIBAN</literal>, <literal>IsIPv4</literal>, <literal>IsLike</literal>, <literal>IsSheetName</literal>, <literal>IsUrl</literal>, <literal>SplitNotQuoted</literal> and <literal>Wrap</literal>."
msgstr "ເນື່ອງຈາກ Python ມີການຮອງຮັບສະຕຣິງໃນຕົວທີ່ຄົບຖ້ວນຢູ່ແລ້ວ, ເມທອດສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ໃນບໍລິການ <literal>String</literal> ຈຶ່ງມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ສະເພາະໃນສະຄຣິບ Basic ເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ເມທອດທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ທັງໃນ Basic ແລະ Python ແມ່ນ: <literal>HashStr</literal>, <literal>IsADate</literal>, <literal>IsEmail</literal>, <literal>IsFileName</literal>, <literal>IsIBAN</literal>, <literal>IsIPv4</literal>, <literal>IsLike</literal>, <literal>IsSheetName</literal>, <literal>IsUrl</literal>, <literal>SplitNotQuoted</literal> ແລະ <literal>Wrap</literal>."

#. jaBZR
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id271579683706571\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Capitalizes the first character from each word in the input string."
msgstr "ປ່ຽນຕົວອັກສອນທຳອິດຂອງແຕ່ລະຄຳໃນສະຕຣິງໃຫ້ເປັນຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່."

#. ibgky
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id941582304592013\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to be capitalized."
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະປ່ຽນເປັນຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່."

#. DB982
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id891582384556756\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Counts the number of occurrences of a substring or a regular expression within a string."
msgstr "ນັບຈຳນວນຄັ້ງທີ່ພົບຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍ ຫຼື regular expression ພາຍໃນສະຕຣິງ."

#. DxK5L
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id571582384689863\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The input string to be examined"
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງຂາເຂົ້າທີ່ຈະກວດສອບ"

#. QUeur
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id601582384696486\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>substring</emph>: The substring or the regular expression to be used during search"
msgstr "<emph>substring</emph>: ຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍ ຫຼື regular expression ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ໃນການຄົ້ນຫາ"

#. vGiqm
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id451582384703719\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>isregex</emph>: Use <literal>True</literal> if the substring is a regular expression (Default = <literal>False</literal>)"
msgstr "<emph>isregex</emph>: ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍເປັນ regular expression (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = <literal>False</literal>)"

#. WiFme
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id141582384726168\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>casesensitive</emph>: The search can be case sensitive or not (Default = <literal>False</literal>)."
msgstr "<emph>casesensitive</emph>: ການຄົ້ນຫາສາມາດກຳນົດໃຫ້ຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍມີຄວາມໝາຍຕ່າງກັນຫຼືບໍ່ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = <literal>False</literal>)."

#. QcE5q
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"bas_id371582384749769\n"
"help.text"
msgid "'Counts the occurrences of the substring \"or\" inside the input string (returns 2)"
msgstr "'ນັບຈຳນວນຄັ້ງທີ່ພົບຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍ \"or\" ພາຍໃນສະຕຣິງ (ສົ່ງຄືນ 2)"

#. XXCR4
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"bas_id561582384801586\n"
"help.text"
msgid "'Counts the number of words with only lowercase letters (returns 7)"
msgstr "'ນັບຈຳນວນຄຳທີ່ມີແຕ່ຕົວພິມນ້ອຍ (ສົ່ງຄືນ 7)"

#. zS3nb
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id131612223767126\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To learn more about regular expressions, refer to the Python's documentation on <link href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/library/re.html\">Regular Expression Operations</link>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຮຽນຮູ້ເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບ regular expressions, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງເອກະສານຂອງ Python ໃນ <link href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/library/re.html\">Regular Expression Operations</link>."

#. CCzMc
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id581579687739629\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns <literal>True</literal> if a string ends with a specified substring."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສະຕຣິງລົງທ້າຍດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍທີ່ລະບຸ."

#. cAmFW
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id21612306392239\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The function returns <literal>False</literal> when either the string or the substring have a length = 0 or when the substring is longer than the string."
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນຈະສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>False</literal> ເມື່ອສະຕຣິງ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍມີຄວາມຍາວເທົ່າກັບ 0 ຫຼື ເມື່ອຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍຍາວກວ່າສະຕຣິງ."

#. qk5nE
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id191579861552201\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to be tested."
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະກວດສອບ."

#. ErigR
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id211579861561473\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>substring</emph>: The substring to be searched at the end of <literal>inputstr</literal>."
msgstr "<emph>substring</emph>: ຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍທີ່ຈະຄົ້ນຫາໃນຕອນທ້າຍຂອງ <literal>inputstr</literal>."

#. 4DKkW
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id801579861574009\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>casesensitive</emph>: The search can be case sensitive or not (Default = <literal>False</literal>)."
msgstr "<emph>casesensitive</emph>: ການຄົ້ນຫາສາມາດກຳນົດໃຫ້ຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍມີຄວາມໝາຍຕ່າງກັນຫຼືບໍ່ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = <literal>False</literal>)."

#. gn2F8
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"bas_id811579862998452\n"
"help.text"
msgid "'Returns True because the method was called with the default CaseSensitive = False"
msgstr "'ສົ່ງຄືນ True ເພາະເມທອດຖືກເອີ້ນໃຊ້ດ້ວຍຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ CaseSensitive = False"

#. vJDmx
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"bas_id231579863168747\n"
"help.text"
msgid "'Returns False due to the CaseSensitive parameter"
msgstr "'ສົ່ງຄືນ False ເນື່ອງຈາກພະລາມິເຕີ CaseSensitive"

#. zThMM
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id921585921441429\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Converts linebreaks and tabs contained in the input string to their equivalent escaped sequence (\\\\, \\n, \\r, \\t)."
msgstr ""
"ແປງການຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່ ແລະ ການແທັບທີ່ມີໃນສະຕຣິງໃຫ້ເປັນລຳດັບການຫຼົບຫຼີກທີ່ທຽບເທົ່າ (\\\\, \\n"
", \\r, \\t)."

#. kBiBE
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id9158592144110\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to be converted."
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະແປງ."

#. cpLKD
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"bas_id901585921441483\n"
"help.text"
msgid "'Returns the string \"abc\\n\\tdef\\\\n\""
msgstr ""
"'ສົ່ງຄືນສະຕຣິງ \"abc\\n"
"\\tdef\\\\n"
"\""

#. ADN8M
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id271579868053137\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Replaces Tab characters <literal>Chr(9)</literal> by space characters to replicate the behavior of tab stops."
msgstr "ແທນທີ່ຕົວອັກສອນ Tab <literal>Chr(9)</literal> ດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນຊ່ອງວ່າງ ເພື່ອຈຳລອງພຶດຕິກຳຂອງ tab stops."

#. Eb23Z
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id951579868064344\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If a line break is found, a new line is started and the character counter is reset."
msgstr "ຖ້າພົບການຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່, ແຖວໃໝ່ຈະເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ຕົວນັບຕົວອັກສອນຈະຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໃໝ່."

#. E73Ko
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id231579868290408\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to be expanded"
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະຂະຫຍາຍ"

#. 9dyYc
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id281579868299807\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>tabsize</emph>: This parameter is used to determine the Tab stops using the formula: TabSize + 1, 2 * TabSize + 1 , ... N * TabSize + 1 (Default = 8)"
msgstr "<emph>tabsize</emph>: ພະລາມິເຕີນີ້ໃຊ້ເພື່ອຊອກຫາ Tab stops ໂດຍໃຊ້ສູດ: TabSize + 1, 2 * TabSize + 1, ... N * TabSize + 1 (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = 8)"

#. GUoE8
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id161579874552729\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Replaces all non-printable characters in the input string by a given character."
msgstr "ແທນທີ່ຕົວອັກສອນທັງໝົດທີ່ບໍ່ສາມາດພິມໄດ້ໃນສະຕຣິງດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້."

#. GpHwp
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id431579874633865\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to be searched"
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະຄົ້ນຫາ"

#. GttDN
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id31579874656437\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>replacedby</emph>: Zero, one or more characters that will replace all non-printable characters in <literal>inputstr</literal> (Default = \"\")"
msgstr "<emph>replacedby</emph>: ຕົວອັກສອນສູນ, ຫນຶ່ງ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍຕົວທີ່ຈະມາແທນທີ່ຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ບໍ່ສາມາດພິມໄດ້ທັງໝົດໃນ <literal>inputstr</literal> (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = \"\")"

#. W44TL
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id1001579876228707\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Finds in a string a substring matching a given regular expression."
msgstr "ຄົ້ນຫາຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍໃນສະຕຣິງທີ່ກົງກັບ regular expression ທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້."

#. aq28M
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id131579876314120\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to be searched"
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະຄົ້ນຫາ"

#. hRrBB
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id751579876371545\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>regex</emph>: The regular expression"
msgstr "<emph>regex</emph>: regular expression ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້"

#. y2Fqs
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id881579876394584\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>start</emph>: The position in the string where the search will begin. This parameter is passed by reference, so after execution the value of <literal>start</literal> will point to the first character of the found substring. If no matching substring is found, <literal>start</literal> will be set to 0."
msgstr "<emph>start</emph>: ຕຳແໜ່ງໃນສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະເລີ່ມການຄົ້ນຫາ. ພະລາມິເຕີນີ້ຖືກສົ່ງຜ່ານດ້ວຍການອ້າງອີງ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນຫຼັງຈາກປະມວນຜົນແລ້ວ ຄ່າຂອງ <literal>start</literal> ຈະຊີ້ໄປຫາຕົວອັກສອນທຳອິດຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍທີ່ພົບ. ຖ້າບໍ່ພົບຂໍ້ຄວາມຍ່ອຍທີ່ກົງກັນ, <literal>start</literal> ຈະຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 0."

#. yZMDg
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id251579876403831\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>casesensitive</emph>: The search can be case sensitive or not (Default = <literal>False</literal>)."
msgstr "<emph>casesensitive</emph>: ການຄົ້ນຫາສາມາດກຳນົດໃຫ້ຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍມີຄວາມໝາຍຕ່າງກັນຫຼືບໍ່ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = <literal>False</literal>)."

#. A4JC7
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id841579876412287\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>forward</emph>: Determines the direction of the search. If <literal>True</literal>, search moves forward. If <literal>False</literal> search moves backwards (Default = <literal>True</literal>)"
msgstr "<emph>forward</emph>: ກຳນົດທິດທາງຂອງການຄົ້ນຫາ. ຖ້າເປັນ <literal>True</literal>, ການຄົ້ນຫາຈະໄປທາງໜ້າ. ຖ້າເປັນ <literal>False</literal>, ການຄົ້ນຫາຈະຖອຍຫຼັງ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ = <literal>True</literal>)"

#. SkaCi
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id451612309155653\n"
"help.text"
msgid "At the first iteration, if <literal>forward = True</literal>, then <literal>start</literal> should be equal to 1, whereas if <literal>forward = False</literal> then <literal>start</literal> should be equal to <literal>Len(inputstr)</literal>"
msgstr "ໃນການເຮັດວຽກຮອບທຳອິດ, ຖ້າ <literal>forward = True</literal>, ຄ່າ <literal>start</literal> ຄວນເທົ່າກັບ 1, ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຖ້າ <literal>forward = False</literal> ຄ່າ <literal>start</literal> ຄວນເທົ່າກັບ <literal>Len(inputstr)</literal>"

#. gv3oo
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id221612309579001\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the example above, the new value of <literal>lStart</literal> can be used to keep searching the same input string by setting the <literal>Start</literal> parameter to <literal>lStart + Len(result)</literal> at the next iteration."
msgstr "ໃນຕົວຢ່າງຂ້າງເທິງ, ຄ່າໃໝ່ຂອງ <literal>lStart</literal> ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອຄົ້ນຫາໃນສະຕຣິງເດີມຕໍ່ໄປໄດ້ ໂດຍການຕັ້ງພະລາມິເຕີ <literal>Start</literal> ເປັນ <literal>lStart + Len(result)</literal> ໃນຮອບຖັດໄປ."

#. qAkN4
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id471601048983628\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hash functions are used inside some cryptographic algorithms, in digital signatures, message authentication codes, manipulation detection, fingerprints, checksums (message integrity check), hash tables, password storage and much more."
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນ Hash ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃນອັນກໍຣິທຶມການເຂົ້າລະຫັດລັບ, ລາຍເຊັນດີຈີຕອນ, ລະຫັດຢືນຢັນຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ການກວດສອບການປ່ຽນແປງຂໍ້ມູນ, ລາຍນິ້ວມືດີຈີຕອນ, ເຊັກຊຳ (checksums), ຕາຕະລາງ hash, ການເກັບຮັກສາລະຫັດຜ່ານ ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ."

#. HupGD
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id301601048983765\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <literal>HashStr</literal> method returns the result of a hash function applied on a given string and using a specified algorithm, as a string of lowercase hexadecimal digits."
msgstr "ເມທອດ <literal>HashStr</literal> ສົ່ງຄືນຜົນລັບຂອງຟັງຊັນ hash ທີ່ໃຊ້ກັບສະຕຣິງທີ່ໃຫ້ມາໂດຍໃຊ້ອັນກໍຣິທຶມທີ່ລະບຸ, ໃນຮູບແບບສະຕຣິງຂອງເລກຖານສິບຫົກຕົວພິມນ້ອຍ."

#. ZRZEF
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id631601048983149\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The hash algorithms supported are: <literal>MD5</literal>, <literal>SHA1</literal>, <literal>SHA224</literal>, <literal>SHA256</literal>, <literal>SHA384</literal> and <literal>SHA512</literal>."
msgstr "ອັນກໍຣິທຶມ hash ທີ່ຮອງຮັບແມ່ນ: <literal>MD5</literal>, <literal>SHA1</literal>, <literal>SHA224</literal>, <literal>SHA256</literal>, <literal>SHA384</literal> ແລະ <literal>SHA512</literal>."

#. yUmmb
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id621601048983210\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to hash. It is presumed to be encoded in UTF-8. The hashing algorithm will consider the string as a stream of bytes."
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະເຮັດ hash. ສົມມຸດວ່າມັນຖືກເຂົ້າລະຫັດເປັນ UTF-8. ອັນກໍຣິທຶມ hashing ຈະພິຈາລະນາສະຕຣິງເປັນສະຕຣີມຂອງໄບຕ໌ (stream of bytes)."

#. nuQRb
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id941601048983822\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>algorithm</emph>: One of the supported algorithms listed above, passed as a string."
msgstr "<emph>algorithm</emph>: ໜຶ່ງໃນອັນກໍຣິທຶມທີ່ຮອງຮັບຕາມລາຍການຂ້າງເທິງ, ໂດຍສົ່ງເປັນສະຕຣິງ."

#. TXGmB
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id221579879516929\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Encodes the input string into the HTML character codes, replacing special characters by their <literal>&</literal> counterparts."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າລະຫັດສະຕຣິງຂາເຂົ້າໃຫ້ເປັນລະຫັດຕົວອັກສອນ HTML, ໂດຍແທັນທີ່ຕົວອັກສອນພິເສດດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ເລີ່ມດ້ວຍ <literal>&</literal> ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. YNfid
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id341612351999692\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example, the character <literal>é</literal> would be replaced by <literal>&eacute;</literal> or an equivalent numerical HTML code."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຕົວອັກສອນ <literal>é</literal> ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍ <literal>&eacute;</literal> ຫຼື ລະຫັດຕົວເລກ HTML ທີ່ທຽບເທົ່າ."

#. CGFQH
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"bas_id501579879570781\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to encode."
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະເຂົ້າລະຫັດ."

#. jpv97
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id171579880990533\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns <literal>True</literal> if the input string is a valid date according to a specified date format."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>True</literal> ຖ້າສະຕຣິງຂາເຂົ້າເປັນວັນທີທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງຕາມຮູບແບບວັນທີທີ່ລະບຸ."

#. tBGBH
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id151579881091821\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>inputstr</emph>: The string to be checked. If empty, the method returns <literal>False</literal>"
msgstr "<emph>inputstr</emph>: ສະຕຣິງທີ່ຈະກວດສອບ. ຖ້າວ່າງເປົ່າ, ເມທອດຈະສົ່ງຄືນ <literal>False</literal>"

#. nmTv3
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id991579881107670\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>dateformat</emph>: The date format, as a string. It can be either \"YYYY-MM-DD\" (default), \"DD-MM-YYYY\" or \"MM-DD-YYYY\""
msgstr "<emph>dateformat</emph>: ຮູບແບບວັນທີ, ເປັນສະຕຣິງ. ສາມາດເປັນ \"YYYY-MM-DD\" (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ), \"DD-MM-YYYY\" ຫຼື \"MM-DD-YYYY\""

#. GvZLC
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id291579881117126\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The dash (-) may be replaced by a dot (.), a slash (/) or a space."
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຂີດ (-) ອາດຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຈຸດ (.), ເຄື່ອງໝາຍທັບ (/) ຫຼື ຊ່ອງວ່າງ."

#. yCA3T
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id51579881125801\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the format is invalid, the method returns <literal>False</literal>."
