#. 6B2Em
#: sf_string.xhp
msgctxt ""
"sf_string.xhp\n"
"par_id211612370427721\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This method checks the format of the input string without performing any calendar-specific checks. Hence it does not test the input string for leap years or months with 30 or 31 days. For that, refer to the <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03102300.xhp\"><literal>IsDate</literal> built-in function</link>."
msgstr "ເມທອດນີ້ຈະກວດສອບພຽງແຕ່ຮູບແບບຂອງສະຕຣິງຂາເຂົ້າ ໂດຍບໍ່ໄດ້ກວດສອບລາຍລະອຽດສະເພາະຂອງປະຕິທິນ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ມັນຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ກວດສອບປີອະທິກະສຸຣະທິນ ຫຼື ເດືອນທີ່ມີ 30 ຫຼື 31 ວັນ. ສຳລັບການກວດສອບນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງທີ່ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03102300.xhp\"><literal>IsDate</literal> built-in function</link>."

